cess to essential services . \\\\n 9. stimulates job creation \\\\n infrastructure projects funded by the bri create jobs in both construction and related industries . local workers are employed to build roads , bridges , railways , and power plants , while businesses benefit from increased demand for materials and services . these job opportunities can boost local economies , reduce unemployment , and improve living standards in participating c\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"20 Pros And Cons Of The Belt And Road Initiative\\\",\\\"pos_rune\\\":[1719],\\\"tag_title\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"search_empty\\\":0,\\\"start_index\\\":1179}\"}]},\"message_id\":\"1930511204725250\",\"local_message_id\":\"c9f5b920-01c3-11f0-aca0-8d7c166c27af\",\"conversation_id\":\"1938602092459522\",\"local_conversation_id\":\"local_6319440182276925\",\"section_id\":\"1938602092459778\",\"reply_id\":\"1930511204724994\",\"is_delta\":true,\"status\":4,\"input_content_type\":2001,\"message_index\":2,\"bot_id\":\"7338286299411103781\"}","event_id":"48","event_type":2001}

